These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, sports, disaster, spy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, dubstep, soul, pop
There are 4 different nationalities: french, australian, british, german
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, airplane, roller, snowmobile
1. the australian is the fan of pop##1
2. the british is between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching spy movies##2
3. the australian is the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
5. the fan of d&b is on the left of the french##1
6. the person driving the roller is the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
8. the french is on the far right##1
9. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | spy   | animation  | disaster  |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | pop    | d&b      | soul    |
| Nationality   | german | australian | british | french |
| Transport     | snowmobile  | taxi       | airplane    | roller     |

