.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, puzzles, gardening, filmmaking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, superhero, spy, mystery
4 different pets are kept: pony, goldfish, fish, hamster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, skateboarding, cricket, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the hamster is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is between the owner of the fish and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
6. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person watching mystery movies and the owner of the hamster##2
7. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
8. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
9. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | puzzles    | gardening  | skydiving    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama      | superhero  | mystery  | spy |
| Pet           | hamster      | fish       | goldfish      | pony       |
| Sport         | skateboarding    | skiing | cricket | weightlifting |

