.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, eggplant, grapes, peas
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, dancing, drawing, video-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, teacher, librarian, fisherman
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, ship, skateboard, boat
1. the librarian is the person driving the ship##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the teacher is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
7. the person eating peas is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
8. the person eating broccoli is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
9. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person eating grapes and the teacher##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | eggplant | grapes     | broccoli   | peas     |
| Hobby       | dancing   | woodworking   | drawing | video-games |
| Job         | accountant   | librarian | fisherman       | teacher    |
| Transport   | skateboard    | ship | bus  | boat    |

