 3. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the ferret##1
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 7. the person watching superhero movies is the dancer##1
 8. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the librarian is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
10. the analyst is between the owner of the goldfish and the entrepreneur##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | librarian  | entrepreneur | analyst     | dancer |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | family  | drama | superhero       |
| Pet           | ferret       | chinchilla    | horse      | goldfish           |
| Sport         | rowing | cycling   | lacrosse   | biathlon         |

