 6. the person eating potato is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 7. the librarian is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
 8. the project-manager is the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the person eating potato is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person watching animation movies##2
10. the person watching sports movies is the person who's sport is skiing##1

