 4. the fan of gospel is the person driving the motorbike##1
 5. the pakistani is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 6. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the indian is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the fan of country is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
10. the american is the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
