4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person driving the van is between the person driving the train and the person watching superhero movies##2
6. the person drinking milk is the person watching animation movies##1
7. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
| Beverage      | milk  | 7up   | almond-milk    | coffee  |
| Movie-Genre   | animation    | family   | superhero | martial-arts |
| Pet           | rat       | guinea-pig   | mouse        | goldfish  |
