 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the owner of the pony is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating orange##2
 9. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating orange##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
