 3. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 5. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the cat##2
 6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 7. the person who's sport is swimming is the person eating pineapple##1
 8. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the cat is the person driving the airplane##1
10. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food        | avocado  | pineapple | raspberry     | spinach     |
| Pet         | cat | rabbit | chinchilla     | bird |
| Sport       | skiing  | swimming   | water-polo | cycling    |
